---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Research — Living Notebook">
  <section class="container mx-auto py-16 px-4">
    <h1 class="text-5xl font-garamond mb-8 text-center text-prime-gold">Research</h1>
    <p class="text-xl mb-12 text-center max-w-3xl mx-auto italic">
      The living notebook of PrimeFlux discoveries — auto-published from Markdown notes. 
      Like a garden journal that grows with each observation.
    </p>
    
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto space-y-8">
      <article class="border border-prime-gold/30 rounded-lg p-8">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4 text-prime-gold">December 4, 2025 — The Site Launches</h2>
        <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed mb-4">
          Tonight, apoptosisai.com goes live — carrying the full weight of PrimeFlux, the ethics of STEM + LANG = SAFE, 
          and the vision for PrimeFlux-Ai. Like seeds planted in fertile soil, the foundation is set.
        </p>
        <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed">
          The thesis is downloadable. The agents are ready. The future begins — not with competition, but with cooperation. 
          Like roots and branches in symbiosis, we extend human capability without replacing human purpose.
        </p>
        <p class="text-sm text-prime-gold/80 mt-4 italic">
          This is not to win. This is to cooperate.
        </p>
      </article>
      
      <div class="text-center p-6 border border-prime-gold/30 rounded-lg">
        <p class="text-lg">
          Add your notes as Markdown in <code class="bg-prime-blue px-2 py-1 rounded">/src/content/blog</code> → auto-publishes.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="text-center mt-16 py-8 border-t border-prime-gold/30">
      <p class="text-2xl font-garamond italic text-prime-gold">
        This is not to win.<br>This is to cooperate.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
